339
00:20:08.548 --> 00:20:12.048
T cells can generate factors that can

340
00:20:12.528 --> 00:20:15.688
remodel the ECM. Blocking BMP1

341
00:20:16.448 --> 00:20:17.988
in combination with immunotherapy,

342
00:20:18.808 --> 00:20:22.488
it can sensitize tumors that are otherwise resistant to

343
00:20:22.528 --> 00:20:26.008
immunotherapy. And tumor ECM remodeling was found

344
00:20:26.108 --> 00:20:29.828
also in clinical samples using head

345
00:20:29.888 --> 00:20:33.748
neck squamous cell carcinoma. And we propose here

346
00:20:33.968 --> 00:20:37.868
first in class, first time antibody drug conjugate

347
00:20:38.348 --> 00:20:42.088
that encompass a PD-1 with an inhibitor of

348
00:20:43.468 --> 00:20:46.718
ECM remodeling enzymes, the BMP1, in

349
00:20:46.808 --> 00:20:50.448
order to make resistant tumors to immunotherapy become

350
00:20:50.568 --> 00:20:54.428
sensitive. And I would like to thank the people that were

