00:48:10.732 --> 00:48:13.792
lab. But I want to thank everyone. Dr.

820
00:48:13.872 --> 00:48:17.482
Kelly Couton did a lot of this work, along with John Passamonte as well,

821
00:48:18.112 --> 00:48:21.202
all of our collaborators at Fox Chase. And then thanks to Dr.

822
00:48:21.412 --> 00:48:25.072
George Zhu, who is our kind of collaborator on the human side of NK

823
00:48:25.152 --> 00:48:25.472
cells.

