00:49:23.072 --> 00:49:26.512
functional redundancies with just ARG1. That is definitely one factor.

843
00:49:26.552 --> 00:49:30.412
What I didn't have time to show today is that the melanoma cells are also

844
00:49:30.432 --> 00:49:34.192
secreting factors like PROS1, and this is really dramatically

845
00:49:34.272 --> 00:49:36.912
increasing myeloid cell infiltration as well.

846
00:49:37.412 --> 00:49:39.952
So it's not just the ARG1 and the aged lung.

