00:49:40.012 --> 00:49:43.012
I think that's one of the factors that maybe allows these things to grow out

848
00:49:43.392 --> 00:49:47.212
efficiently initially. But then I think the melanoma cells take over and

849
00:49:47.292 --> 00:49:49.542
start to secrete, not only some of these factors.

