00:50:04.392 --> 00:50:08.112
colonization, not dormancy. We have some of that kind of

855
00:50:08.132 --> 00:50:09.572
dormancy effect going in the lung.

856
00:50:09.652 --> 00:50:13.352
The only way we can really look at it, though, is putting mCherry in, and this does

