00:50:47.732 --> 00:50:51.452
fluorescent protein on top of H2B, and we could

868
00:50:51.492 --> 00:50:54.672
basically track whether or not these cells are growing out over time or if they

869
00:50:54.692 --> 00:50:56.812
remain dormant, and we have FUCCI with that as well.

870
00:50:56.872 --> 00:50:58.652
So I'm happy to discuss that afterwards.

871
00:50:58.732 --> 00:51:02.012
But yeah, in terms of the dormancy side, we're trying to get to that stage, but

872
00:51:02.092 --> 00:51:04.432
right now we're more on the colonization side of things.

873
00:51:04.892 --> 00:51:06.092
Okay. Adriana?

